articles.title: Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 6 Rumored To Get LPDDR6 RAM & UFS 5.0 Support For Faster AI Operations, But Tipster Shares Questionable Lithography Details - Wccftech
articles.description: A tipster provides early information on the Snapdragon 8 Elite Gen 6, claiming that apart from LPDDR6 RAM and UFS 5.0 support, it will be made on TSMC's 2nm N2P node
